        "docstring": {
          "summary": "Adjust the number of bins to meet minimum and multiple constraints.",
          "description": "Adjust the number of bins to meet minimum and multiple constraints.\n\nThis method preserves the existing bin packing as much as possible and only\nmoves sequences one at a time to create additional bins when needed.",
